<br>
1.) Save up, the bazaar is your friend.<br>
<br>
2.) In your 50's, Umbral Planes, mobs (Moktors) drop some decent upgrade armor for Wars and they are doable with one solid group. I can't get PU groups there  now since PoP.  Zones like Seb, are practically empty now, also very doable with a single solid group of 50s.  Decent exp, and better sellable loot.<br>
<br>
